      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box collapse\">\n\t\t\t我對這個問題有超額的話語權，<br/>\n<br/>\n東亞審美，尤其是日本的審美，主要是因爲這個人，詳情請看關於這位的紀錄片和書，<br/>\n而日本的流行文化又影響了全亞洲，<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9FZ0pQSHlHLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/EgJPHyG.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/EgJPHyG.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/EgJPHyG.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n這種永恆的美少年特質，又是來源於古羅馬和古希臘（上面這位就是被這樣描述的，所以導演也是這麽去尋找的）<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS96RjQ3cURTLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/zF47qDS.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/zF47qDS.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zF47qDS.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9wVlRvbG5uLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/pVTolnn.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/pVTolnn.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pVTolnn.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n我自己作爲同類很是清楚，<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9tUldFSnp3LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/mRWEJzw.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/mRWEJzw.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mRWEJzw.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n某比利時攝影師如此稱贊過，說這樣的人裸體搭配著跑車，如同駕著chariot的裸體阿波羅一樣美，<br/>\n比如下圖<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9QUjBzcHJvLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/PR0spro.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/PR0spro.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PR0spro.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n我還覺得，作爲如此恐同的國家，紙幣正面還出現了正面裸露男性性器官的模樣十分諷刺滑稽，我再也想不到別的國家有出現男性性器官的錢幣，<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9mWHhkWjVhLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/fXxdZ5a.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/fXxdZ5a.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fXxdZ5a.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9UcGp1M1V3LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/Tpju3Uw.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Tpju3Uw.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Tpju3Uw.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n我就不親自裸體示範了，水邊玩耍略作表示，<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9tc0xKNERSLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/msLJ4DR.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/msLJ4DR.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/msLJ4DR.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9uVVA4NzkzLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/nUP8793.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/nUP8793.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nUP8793.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS95RDBLaG9vLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/yD0Khoo.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/yD0Khoo.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yD0Khoo.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9DOUNxcXRnLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/C9Cqqtg.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/C9Cqqtg.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/C9Cqqtg.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n這樣的審美並不只是亞洲才有，歐洲和美洲大部分的時候審美也吻合於此，<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9